* Here, you can find all the files reporting the results obtained by each partner while performing the CNRS benchmark.
This folder is meant to complete the manuscript 
Tiberga M. et al., "Results from a multi-physics numerical benchmark for codes dedicated to molten salt fast reactors", Annals of Nuclear Energy.

* In each subfolder, you can find the files with the profiles along the relevant centerline for all the observables in that step.

